name: NFT MANIFESTO
description:
Kush Nubia: Non-Fungible Token [NFT] Manifesto

My purpose is to unite the world through art and music, adding to positive consciousness, a healthy planet and active communities

I believe that reaching back to the foundation of ancestry and culture is necessary to create a cohesive, vibrant community and important for elementary development.

I believe that NFT collectable artwork owned by the community can be an anchor for building community wealth.

Therefore; I believe that works of art, visual or otherwise, should be created and supported by members of a community providing  important reminders and symbols of cohesiveness.

In memory of those before us, a percentage of all of my independent NFT creations will be sent to the Mount Ward Alumni Association non-profit organization to assist the school in improving educational facilities, the learning environment, and opportunities for its students.
